    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span><em>You can expend a bardic inspiration die to blast nearby creatures with magical and extremely loud noise.</em></span></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 20 ft. Cone - Magical - 1 Round</p><p>When you use this ability, you end the silenced condition on yourself, and dispel any magical zones of silence in the area that are eligible to be dispelled by<em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.oZwKW3I3yzrSdpLE]{Dispel Magic}</em>.</p><p><span><strong>Constitution</strong> </span><strong>Save</strong> (DC Equal to Bard Spells)</p><ul><li><p><span><strong>Failure</strong> </span>: &amp;reference[thunder] damage equal to four rolls of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die and target is &amp;reference[deafened].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Action</strong> - 20 ft. Cone - Magical - 1 Round</p><p>When you use this ability, you end the silenced condition on yourself, and dispel any magical zones of silence in the area that are eligible to be dispelled by <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.oZwKW3I3yzrSdpLE]{Dispel Magic}</em>.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Constitution</strong></span> Save (DC Equal to Bard Spells)</p><ul class=\"font_8\"><li><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Failure</strong></span>: &amp;reference[thunder] damage equal to four rolls of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{bardic inspiration} die and target is &amp;reference[deafened].</p></li><li><p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><strong>Success</strong></span>: Half damage.</p></li></ul>"
        },
